xx.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GOLDEN_PLACE_BODY_DESC: Place the body of Naadim Yacoub in the Maintenence Storage Room
xx.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GOLDEN_DOUBLE_WHAMMY_DES: Pacify and then eliminate Zana “The Vulture” Kazemi. If he is killed without being pacified first, mission will fail.

en.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GOLDEN_PLACE_BODY_DESC: Place the body of Naadim Yacoub in the Maintenence Storage Room
en.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GOLDEN_DOUBLE_WHAMMY_DES: Pacify and then eliminate Zana “The Vulture” Kazemi. If he is killed without being pacified first, mission will fail.

fr.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GOLDEN_PLACE_BODY_DESC: Placez le corps de Naadim Yacoub dans la réserve de maintenance.
fr.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GOLDEN_DOUBLE_WHAMMY_DES: Neutralisez puis éliminez Zana Kazem, dit "le Vautour". S'il est assassiné sans avoir été d'abord neutralisé, la mission échoue.

it.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GOLDEN_PLACE_BODY_DESC: Metti il corpo di Naadim Yacoub nella sala della manutenzione
it.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GOLDEN_DOUBLE_WHAMMY_DES: Neutralizza e poi elimina Zana "l'Avvoltoio" Kazem. Se verrà eliminato senza essere prima stato neutralizzato, la missione fallirà.

de.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GOLDEN_PLACE_BODY_DESC: Platzieren Sie die Leiche von Naadim Yacoub im Wartungslagerraum.
de.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GOLDEN_DOUBLE_WHAMMY_DES: Stellen Sie Zana „den Geier“ Kazemi ruhig und eliminieren Sie ihn dann. Wird er getötet, ohne ruhiggestellt zu werden, scheitert die Mission.

es.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GOLDEN_PLACE_BODY_DESC: Mete el cuerpo de Naadim Yacoub en el almacén de mantenimiento
es.UI_GAMECHANGERS_GOLDEN_DOUBLE_WHAMMY_DES: Deja inconsciente y luego elimina a Zana Kazem, «El Buitre». Si lo matas sin dejarlo inconsciente previamente, la misión fracasará.
